{"tid":1550600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有黑社會用鐵棍扑人頭,警察唔到現場拾證物","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:59.000Z","uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"318a60eb5ee7dffa5e14f237f63e9a96ae51b1f4","tid":1550600,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nr4zdvmG9oI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNr4zdvmG9oI&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQCz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=1b42ec3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nr4zdvmG9oI</a><br />\n<br />\n有傷者<br />\n有證人<br />\n點到黑社會相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\nCID故意唔收證物放黑社會</span>"},{"pid":"52ac5e2129256c5db1a255292f3cb92aa9003a16","tid":1550600,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"拉去10分鐘前睇"},{"pid":"5cde64b5c571ae57aca9dbc9089976c836599bed","tid":1550600,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:46:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3f0f1cce1b841b2f42e056ce03616721f8163b9e","tid":1550600,"uid":241331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:49:59.000Z","msg":"至各位Mon Post 你班差佬究竟有冇諗過<br />\n你地咁樣幫個政權維穩 毒打市民 製造恐懼 將香港社會同中共同化 <br />\n對你下一代下二代有咩影響? <br />\n你確定到你上到岸之餘你下一代都可以上岸? 定係你確定到你既仔女都可以做返警察?<br />\n定係你確定你夠錢成家移民?<br />\n<br />\n唔好將香港變大陸"}]}